Body: Description: Need to check general dashboard graph is correct or accurate. Some of the activities showing high on specific date for on general dashboard. Kindly need your support to check this.

Steps to Reproduce Updated: - have log activity
- check the General Dashboard to the graphic representation of those events

What We've Learned Updated: - I asked the user to filter the dashboard by date and to check the logs if these are indeed showing up in the general dashboard correlated with what he sees in the Report&Analysis section.
Next Steps Updated: Perform a follow-up to see if he could check the recommendation
